Thy leaves are so...

872
01:18:20.353 --> 01:18:22.938
Must've got wet coming over.

873
01:18:23.690 --> 01:18:26.435
I don't see how you ever
managed to get it ashore.


874
01:18:26.535 --> 01:18:30.079
Anh không làm một mình.
Fritz và Ernst đã giúp anh.


875
01:18:37.963 --> 01:18:40.157
Giáng Sinh vui vẻ.

876
01:18:40.257 --> 01:18:41.966
Merry Christmas.

877
