Thy leaves are so unchanging

895
01:20:19.773 --> 01:20:21.800
Anh mang gì về vậy?

896
01:20:21.900 --> 01:20:24.469
Chúng con nghĩ mẹ còn thức!

897
01:20:24.569 --> 01:20:26.471
- Hey!
- Merry Christmas!


898
01:20:26.571 --> 01:20:28.432
Merry Christmas!

899
01:20:28.532 --> 01:20:30.809
- Francis.
- Merry Christmas.


